[Website Files]

This ZIP file contains:
1. **index.html** - The main structure of your website.
2. **styles.css** - Styling for an attractive design.
3. **images/** - A folder for your product images (you can add more later).

### Steps to Upload to GitHub:
1. Extract the ZIP file on your computer.
2. Go to your GitHub repository.
3. Click **"Add file" > "Upload files"**.
4. Drag and drop the extracted files.
5. Click **"Commit changes"** to save.

Once uploaded, share the GitHub repository link with me so I can deploy it on Netlify!
